sentences.english: Now it’s time to preplan your trip.
sentences.chinese: 現在，是時候提前計劃你的行程了。

sentences.english: The flywheels of some engines also carry marks indicating the serial numbers of the cylinders where the compression occurs.

sentences.english: You can plan your road trip itinerary for the schedule you need to keep.
sentences.chinese: 你可以把自駕遊計劃與你的行程安排保持一致。

sentences.english: Early that day, during what was a weeklong trip to China, she visited Mr.

sentences.english: Sakyamuni was thus able to continue his journey.

sentences.english: When you get to the end of your route, turn around and walk in the opposite direction until you get to the starting point.

sentences.english: The five-day trip was wonderful and it covered nearly 1, 500km.

sentences.english: Mission Control has it all for the long travel single crown fork.

sentences.english: Sixteen hours and I wanted to cry with boredom.

sentences.english: In the evening, we will end our trip at Juzizhou Park.
sentences.chinese: 到了晚上，我們將結束我們的行程在橘子洲公園。

sentences.english: So we want to write programs to do that.

sentences.english: The independent India rate schedule design, facilitates to adjust the machine speed.
sentences.chinese: 獨立印頭行程設計，方便速度調節。

sentences.english: Transfer to Airport and home your sweet home.
sentences.chinese: 早餐後，按指定時間前往機場送機，結束愉快的行程。

sentences.english: The trip takes three months in total.

sentences.english: Instead, they deal with the abstract login interface that the callable routine provides.
